						</div>
					</li>
					<li class="home-item">
						<figure class="home-testimony-visuel"><img src="images/171.jpg" alt="R."></figure>     	
						<div class="home-item-content">
							<blockquote>Après une licence scientifique générale, je voulais intégrer la vie professionnelle. J’ai pensé que la visite médicale me conviendrait et pendant quel</blockquote>
							<p class="author">Vincent R.</p>
						</div>
					</li>
				</ul>

				<p class="block-action"><a href="http://alternativespro.fr/temoignages" class="border-btn round-btn light-btn">Autres témoignages</a></p>
			</div>
		</section>
		

		<section class="contact">
			<div class="content-wrap">
				<h2>Poser votre question</h2>
				<form action="/emailing" method="post">
					<div class="interactive-label">
						<label for="project_appli_emailing_email" class="required">Votre email</label>
						<input id="project_appli_emailing_email" name="project_appli_emailing[email]" required="required" class="form-control hide-label" type="text">                
					</div>
					<div class="interactive-label">
						<label for="project_appli_emailing_object" class="required">Objet</label>
						<textarea id="project_appli_emailing_object" name="project_appli_emailing[object]" required="required" class="form-control hide-label"></textarea>                
					</div>
					<p class="action"><input id="submit" name="submit" value="Envoyer" class="round-btn" type="submit"></p>
					<input id="project_appli_emailing__token" name="project_appli_emailing[_token]" value="zcMN75WdMz7AJkLeqRNKhGMvY1msgeGFg7XAXO5L1qo" type="hidden">
				</form>
			</div>
		</section>               
